Booster knows that the Flashpoint world isn't his own. But how does he get back? How does he make things right?

After rescuing a woman during his battle against Doomsday, Booster gets the shock of a lifetime when he discovers the monster is controlled by Nathaniel Adam aslo known as Captain Atom. He also uses his computer skills to determine the changes to this new reality and how they came to pass. He's on the trail for clues regarding the chronal changes when he's suddenly and savagely attacked again by Doosmday.
2011-06-06|2011-06-12.name: Turbulence, Part Two

2011-08-15|2011-08-21.description:
While the war for Asgard rages there’s always time for a grudge match or two. Cue Spider-Man versus Venom! ‘Nuff said!

Also, As the Gauntlet rages on around him, the spotlight is on Peter Parker’s original archenemy-turned-best friend, Flash Thompson. Since losing his legs in service to his country, Flash Thompson’s not been deterred by his physical limitations. But even a hero can have his limits. Plus, Spider-Man comes face-to-face with Morbius, The Living Vampire!

Plus, classic action, as the Assassination Nation Plot continues! With the C.I.A. implicated in the urder of Symkaria’s prime minister and the king’s fiancée it’s down to Spider-Man and Captain America to hunt down the real killers!

Includes material reprinted from Siege: Spider-Man, Amazing Spider-Man #622 ,Amazing Spider-Man #323 and Web of Spider-Man Vol.2 #4.

2011-10-10|2011-10-16.description: You are invited to a special Batgirl issue featuring Cassandra, Stephanie, Flamebird and, of course, Barbara. Find out what happens to The Batcave when the girls take over! Bonus: Coach Lobo's Secret Soccer team versus…The Birds of Prey?! GO-O-O-A-A-AL!

Two hundred years have passed since Ulf Haukur rose to power and established the Haukursson Clan as a force to be reckoned with. But the wild frontier days of Iceland are long gone. Can the family line continue into more modern and complicated times? "The Icelandic Trilogy" continues with part 4 of 9, titled "Conversion."
2011-10-10|2011-10-16.name: The Icelandic Trilogy, Part 4: Conversion 999

2011-10-24|2011-10-30.description: What would happen if a collection of Deadpool’s frozen, severed body parts were to be thrown into a dumpster and then, once thawed, fuse together to form a new--and totally evil--Deadpool? Well, we could tell you…but it’d be way cooler if you read it for yourself!

2011-12-05|2011-12-11.description: HULK OF ARABIA reaches its astonishing conclusion! One of the most hotly anticipated Red Hulk stories yet has all been building to this! Red and Machine Man go mono a mono (a machino) against Dagan Shah, the mysterious new powerhouse whose mythical kingdom of Sharzhad has become a destabilizing new force to be reckoned with! Mastermind Jeff Parker and the brilliant Patch Zircher guarantee the result of this epic showdown is one you won't see coming, and will change the face of the Marvel universe!
